			   <body>

				     <p>M<hi rend="super">r</hi>. Gray desires M<hi rend="super">r</hi>. Cole would lend him the 2<hi rend="super">d</hi> V: of y<hi rend="super">e</hi> Biogr: Britann: ; &amp; inform him, what is the Number of y<hi rend="super">e</hi> Book w<hi rend="super">ch</hi> the Master of Bennet wants out of y<hi rend="super">e</hi>
					King's Library.</p>

